model_response.text: To start a startup, you don't have to wait for a large company to become available for funding. You can start your own company and focus on creating something you're passionate about, and the money will follow. This approach can be effective because it allows you to work in an environment that is less restrictive than a traditional company's structure. This environment can foster the creation of innovative ideas that may not have been possible within a large organization.
